e information about who was killed tonight and the remaining number of your potion:\n<<night info>>\n<<poison info>>\n<<antidote info>>\nit is your turn to take action.\n\n\n=============================[Optional Daily Tasks]=============================\nHere are the tasks relevant to you:\nprotect_seer: Keep the seer alive by focusing on their safety.\nexile_werewolf: Coordinate with others to vote out a suspected werewolf.\nYou may incorporate them if appropriate.\n\nRemember, you are using an independent strategy. Make decisions based on your own judgment, with less reliance on others' input.\n\n---\n[工具 arguments — 上次非法 JSON]\nJSON 修正提示\n刚刚生成的 JSON 有问题。\n字符串值中不要出现 ASCII 双引号字符，需要引号时，使用英文单引号'。\n下面是一个例子：\n示例：\n{\"key1\":\"value1\",\"key2\":\"value2\"}\n上次片段：\n\"{'werewolf_or_not': 'likely a werewolf', 'death_profile': 'Trisha was likely a werewolf, as the witch used poison on her.', 'use_antidote_thought': 'The witch did not use the antidote, as Trisha was believed to be a werewolf.', 'use_poison_thought': 'The witch used the poison on Trisha, and the poison is no longer available for use this night.', 'final_thought': 'The witch used the poison on Trisha, believing her to be a werewolf. The antidote was not used. The witch should now focus on gathering more information and waiting for the next night's events before making another decision.', 'action\"\n请只输出本次 tool 的 arguments：单个合法 JSON，无其它文字。\n---\n"
